WEBVTT

00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:03.800
"Fruit"

00:00:04.580 --> 00:00:08.030
(Episode 3: Light)

00:00:13.200 --> 00:00:14.200
You're late.

00:00:21.740 --> 00:00:22.740
Easels?

00:00:26.530 --> 00:00:28.500
I found a cat by the awning just now.

00:00:28.500 --> 00:00:30.400
Could someone be secretly feeding it?

00:00:30.500 --> 00:00:31.630
Will you keep it?

00:00:31.630 --> 00:00:32.610
- Or will you turn it in?
- Chips!

00:00:32.610 --> 00:00:33.100
Miss!

00:00:33.120 --> 00:00:34.130
No, cats are too dirty.

00:00:34.130 --> 00:00:35.820
- I'll throw it out.
- I need the restroom.

00:00:45.580 --> 00:00:46.810
Let's get started.

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:49.300
Today we're drawing dark clouds.

00:00:49.300 --> 00:00:50.720
Did everyone bring photos?

00:00:54.990 --> 00:00:56.130
Chips!

00:00:56.130 --> 00:00:57.070
What are you doing?

00:00:57.080 --> 00:00:58.320
Give it back!

00:00:58.440 --> 00:00:59.270
Miss!

00:01:20.470 --> 00:01:21.670
Let's look over there.

00:01:21.670 --> 00:01:24.810
Shh, Chips... keep it down.

00:01:25.130 --> 00:01:27.690
I'll take you somewhere safe.

00:01:42.250 --> 00:01:43.070
Guoshu.

00:01:46.470 --> 00:01:47.850
Are you okay?

00:02:00.090 --> 00:02:00.850
Come here.

00:02:00.850 --> 00:02:02.380
Miss...

00:02:13.750 --> 00:02:16.880
It's okay now.

00:02:21.420 --> 00:02:22.820
It's okay.

00:02:26.370 --> 00:02:27.540
You got hurt?

00:02:34.300 --> 00:02:36.030
Take your shirt off.

00:02:44.710 --> 00:02:45.690
Take it slow.

00:03:03.660 --> 00:03:04.900
No need to take it all off.

00:03:07.120 --> 00:03:08.670
Oh, okay.

00:03:30.910 --> 00:03:32.040
Bear with it.

00:03:32.590 --> 00:03:34.120
It hurts!

00:03:36.110 --> 00:03:38.260
It really hurts...

00:03:46.520 --> 00:03:49.400
I know. Bear with it.

00:04:16.670 --> 00:04:19.720
I can't treat you like this.

00:04:44.970 --> 00:04:45.900
Don't move.

00:05:23.180 --> 00:05:25.620
Try moving it. See if it feels loose.

00:05:25.620 --> 00:05:27.760
Oh.

00:05:36.070 --> 00:05:38.030
Thank you, Miss.

00:06:03.690 --> 00:06:06.890
At the time, she didn't say much.

00:06:07.600 --> 00:06:10.230
Just gently buttoned up my shirt.

00:06:10.570 --> 00:06:14.100
In that moment, I felt her warmth,

00:06:14.530 --> 00:06:17.000
like she was quietly caring for me.

00:06:17.730 --> 00:06:19.550
But at the time...

00:06:19.550 --> 00:06:23.430
- I didn't dare ask what it all meant.
- Try moving.

00:06:23.870 --> 00:06:25.430
I'll take care of Chips.

00:06:26.400 --> 00:06:29.370
Make sure to see a doctor, check that' nothing's broken.

00:06:32.960 --> 00:06:33.960
Then...

00:06:34.800 --> 00:06:35.800
Chips,

00:06:36.610 --> 00:06:38.510
you be good, okay?

00:06:42.120 --> 00:06:45.630
I'll be going now, Miss. Thank you.